                 sm:w-auto sm:bg-transparent sm:text-accent sm:border sm:border-accent sm:hover:bg-accent sm:hover:text-white"
          href="#"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Shop This Style
        </a>
